## Feedback Synthesis Workflow

- [ ] 1. Collect all feedback from all stakeholders
- [ ] 2. Identify each piece of feedback with its source
- [ ] 3. Look for patterns and consensus across sources
- [ ] 4. Distinguish between feedback (observations) and direction (requests)
- [ ] 5. Identify the underlying intent behind the feedback
- [ ] 6. Consolidate into clear, specific action items
- [ ] 7. Flag any conflicting feedback that needs resolution

